    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior and interior show some light signs of regular use, such as minor surface scratches and slight seat wear, the car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It offers a great balance of reliability and value for someone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
