    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that truly embodies the 'good' condition standard. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor, expected stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well. The interior is exceptionally clean and has remained a smoke-free environment; the leather seats show only light softening from use without any cracks or thinning. All onboard electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust. It comes with a comprehensive service history detailing regular oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the engine idles smoothly with no unusual noises. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle perfect for someone who values a well-cared-for daily driver.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle that exemplifies consistent maintenance and reliable performance. This model offers a refined driving experience, balancing mechanical integrity with aesthetic appeal. Meticulously inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards, it represents a premier choice for the discerning driver seeking both quality and value. We invite you to experience this superior engineering firsthand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It has been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, just waiting for its next adventure! I've taken great care of it over the years, so it\u2019s clean, running smoothly, and ready to hit the road today. It's the perfect blend of comfort and dependability. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the mechanical synergy is unparalleled. Critical preventative maintenance has been proactively addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells, and a reinforced rear subframe carrier. The chassis benefits from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain is exceptionally tight, the M-Variable differential locks predictably, and the throttle response remains razor-sharp. A mechanically sorted icon engineered for the purist.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
